---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="How Much Does It Cost to Build in Eastern Idaho? — Odyssey Homes"
  description="It's the first question every buyer asks. Here's the honest answer — and how Odyssey's free online estimator gives you a real number in minutes."
>
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-odyssey-charcoal text-odyssey-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-odyssey-accent-light uppercase">Blog</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white leading-tight">
        How Much Does It Cost to Build in Eastern Idaho?
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-odyssey-cream/85 leading-relaxed">
        It's the first question every buyer asks — and the honest answer is: it depends. Here's how to get a real number fast.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero image -->
  <div class="bg-odyssey-charcoal">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pb-0">
      <div class="aspect-[16/7] overflow-hidden rounded-t-lg">
        <img
          src="/media/blog/estimator-tool-preview.png"
          alt="Odyssey Homes new construction in Eastern Idaho"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Post content -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-20">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none
        prose-headings:text-odyssey-charcoal prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-tight
        prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:lg:text-3xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-4
        prose-h3:text-xl prose-h3:mt-8 prose-h3:mb-3
        prose-p:text-odyssey-stone-dark prose-p:leading-relaxed
        prose-a:text-odyssey-accent prose-a:font-semibold prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline
        prose-strong:text-odyssey-charcoal
        prose-ol:text-odyssey-stone-dark prose-ul:text-odyssey-stone-dark
        prose-li:my-2">

        <p>If you've been searching for a straight answer on what it costs to build a new home in Eastern Idaho, you've probably noticed that nobody wants to give you one. You get vague ranges, disclaimers, and a lot of "it depends."</p>

        <p>Here's the truth: it <strong>does</strong> depend — on the floor plan, the lot, the community, your permit costs, and every upgrade decision you make along the way. Two homes built on the same street by the same builder can have meaningfully different price tags based on the choices made inside them. That's why any single number published on a website would be misleading.</p>

        <p>But <strong>"it depends" isn't good enough</strong> when you're trying to plan your life. You need a real number — and you need it before you sit down with a sales rep, not after.</p>

        <h2>We Built a Tool for This</h2>

        <p>Odyssey Homes developed something we haven't seen any other builder in Eastern Idaho offer: <strong>a fully interactive, self-serve home cost estimator</strong> that lets you build out your complete contract — in real time — before you ever talk to anyone.</p>

        <p><a href="/estimate/">Our Home Quote Estimator</a> isn't a "contact us for pricing" form. It's not a ballpark calculator that spits out a range. It's a step-by-step tool that walks you through exactly what we walk every buyer through in a sales meeting — floor plan selection, lot, permits, and every upgrade category — and shows you a <strong>running total as you go</strong>.</p>

        <p>By the time you're done, you have a complete, itemized cost summary built from our actual prices. Not an estimate of an estimate. The real numbers.</p>

        <h2>How the Estimator Works</h2>

        <p>Head to <a href="/estimate/">buildodyssey.com/estimate</a> and you'll be walked through four steps:</p>

        <ol>
          <li>
            <strong>Pick your floor plan.</strong> Browse Odyssey's full plan lineup — square footage, bedroom count, and base pricing all visible upfront. See exactly what you're starting with before you commit to anything.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Choose your lot and community.</strong> Lot costs vary by community and location within it. <a href="/estimate/">The estimator</a> shows available lots with their actual prices so you're comparing apples to apples.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Add your upgrades.</strong> This is where most of the price variation happens. Walk through every category — cabinets, flooring, countertops, electrical, HVAC, and more — and select your tier. <strong>Your total updates live with every choice you make.</strong>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Get your complete summary.</strong> At the end, you have a full itemized cost breakdown you can review, save, and share with your spouse or financial advisor — before your first conversation with us.
          </li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Why This Changes Everything for Buyers</h2>

        <p>Most buyers walk into a builder's office without any idea what they're about to spend. They fall in love with a floor plan, get excited about upgrades, and then experience sticker shock when the final number comes together. That's a frustrating experience for everyone involved.</p>

        <p><a href="/estimate/">Our estimator</a> flips that entirely. <strong>You come in informed.</strong> You've already made your upgrade decisions, you know what your number looks like, and the conversation with your sales rep can focus on moving forward — not on managing expectations.</p>

        <p>We built this tool ourselves, from the ground up, because we believe buyers deserve transparency. <strong>No other builder in Eastern Idaho gives you this kind of access</strong> before you've committed to anything. It's one of the things we're most proud of, and buyers tell us constantly that it changed how they thought about the process.</p>

        <h2>Ready to See Your Number?</h2>

        <p>Head to <a href="/estimate/">buildodyssey.com/estimate</a> and build your first estimate. It takes about five minutes, it's completely free, and you're not obligated to do anything with it.</p>

        <p>But we think once you see your number — <strong>your real number, built from your actual choices</strong> — the path forward gets a lot clearer.</p>

        <p>Questions after you've run through it? <a href="/lets-talk/">Reach out here</a> and one of our team members will walk through it with you personally.</p>

      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-odyssey-bone rounded-lg text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-odyssey-accent uppercase">Try It Now — It's Free</p>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-odyssey-charcoal">Build Your Estimate in 5 Minutes</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark">No sign-up required. No obligation. Just your real number.</p>
        <a href="/estimate/" class="mt-6 inline-block bg-odyssey-accent hover:bg-odyssey-accent-deep text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded transition-colors">
          Open the Home Quote Estimator →
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-10 text-sm">
        ← <a href="/blog/" class="text-odyssey-accent hover:underline font-semibold">Back to Blog</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
